text: "Midnight Memories" is a 2014 song by English-Irish boy band One Direction and is the third single from their third studio album of the same name. It went to number 2 in Denmark, number 3 in Ireland and New Zealand, number 4 in Belgium, Greece and Spain, number 5 in the Netherlands and Portugal, number 7 in Italy, number 8 in Lebanon, number 12 in the United States, number 14 in France, number 22 in Austria, number 35 in Canada, number 39 in the United Kingdom and number 54 in Australia. == Track listing == Digital download – EP # "Midnight Memories" – 2:55 # "Story of My Life" (Live X Factor performance) – 4:18 # "Rock Me" (Live version from the Motion Picture One Direction: This Is Us) – 4:15 # "C'mon, C'mon" (Live version from the Motion Picture One Direction: This Is Us) – 3:27 == References == Category:2014 songs Category:One Direction songs Category:Pop rock songs
